playstore_details.title: PetPage
playstore_details.description:
PetPage has turned the page to a newer, better, more responsive app to simplify caring for your pet from the palm of your hand.*

The PetPage App features easy-to-use, self-serve tools keeping you connected to your
veterinarian and your pet’s health 24/7:
     - Simple registration and login process
     - Set up and receive in-app notifications and reminders
     - Request appointments – even after hours
     - Request prescription refills anytime, anywhere
     - Share your Pet ID and contact information
     - Easily update your information

*Your veterinarian must be subscribed to PetPage, and you must have an email address on file with them to register in the app. Have questions? Contact your veterinarian today!
